%o A045949 (Magma) [(28*n^3 +18*n^2 +4*n -1 +(-1)^n)/8: n in [0..40]]; // _G. C. Greubel_, Apr 05 2019
%o A045949 (SageMath) [(28*n^3 +18*n^2 +4*n -1 +(-1)^n)/8 for n in (0..40)] # _G. C. Greubel_, Apr 05 2019
